His ajax demo is your first idea: <a href="http://razorjack.net/quicksand/demos/ajax.html" rel="nofollow">http://razorjack.net/quicksand/demos/ajax.html</a><p>You can use the ajax demo to make your second idea. Like this:<p><pre><code>  $(function(){
    $('#load-players a.button').click(function(e){
      $.get(($this).attr('href'), function(data) {
        $('.rank-after').quicksand($(data).find('li'));
      });
    });
  });
</code></pre>
For each link:<p><pre><code>  event-name.html
  <ul class="rank-after">
    <li data-id="1"><img src="federer.png" /></li>
    <li data-id="2"><img src="roddick.png" /></li>
  </ul></code></pre>
